.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_preachers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/manic-street-preachers">Manic Street Preachers</a>在他们的社交媒体上用一段新音乐片段戏弄了新材料 - 请查看下面的片段及其随附的视觉效果。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="468" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/manic-street-preachers-ultra-vivid-lament-nicky-wire-james-dean-bradfield-3020202"><b>狂躁街传教士：“我们通过遗忘来谈论自己”</b></a></li></ul><p>乐队在周一（8 月 26 日）的帖子标题中写道：“关于衰落和堕落就这么多了。”</p><p>这段 20 秒的剪辑以胜利、上升的吉他即兴演奏和疯狂的鼓声为特色，视频剪辑以威尔士诗人迪伦·托马斯的一句话开头：“太阳最高的赞歌是在黑暗中写成的”。</p><p>器乐剪辑因静态中断而结结巴巴，还包括遵循与标题类似模式的短语：“计算就这么多”，“站立得那么好”，“含义就这么多”，最后以相同的方式结束话：“关于衰落和衰落就这么多了”。请看下面。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_I4QSDtB5D/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100p